HEADWORD: Nondo
<hw>Non"do</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A
coarse umbelliferous plant (<spn>Ligusticum actaeifolium</spn>) with a
large aromatic root. It is found chiefly in the Alleghany region. Also
called <altname>Angelico</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

